ld-trump-demands-as-iran-israel-resume-strikes-1st-time-post-april-ceasefire/articleshow/131583880.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T15:34:11+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Yashasvi Vasistha</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131584903,imgsize-52154.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[24 Indian seafarers seek urgent help after vessel reportedly attacked off Oman coast]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131584590.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Twenty-four Indian seafarers are urgently seeking help after their vessel was reportedly attacked off Oman's coast, near the Strait of Hormuz. The Forward Seamen's Union of India has appealed to the Indian Navy and authorities for intervention amidst rising regional tensions. Details regarding the attack and the vessel remain unconfirmed by official sources.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/24-indian-seafarers-seek-urgent-help-after-vessel-reportedly-attacked-off-oman-coast/articleshow/131584590.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/24-indian-seafarers-seek-urgent-help-after-vessel-reportedly-attacked-off-oman-coast/articleshow/131584590.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T15:24:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Ayush Pandey</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131584705,imgsize-37902.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UAE grants 3-day weekend to students, private sector and government employees for Islamic New Year]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131583610.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[UAE residents will enjoy a public holiday on Monday, June 15, 2026