iimg.com/photo/msid-131578624,imgsize-56980.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Thank you, darling': Trump storms out of NBC interview after calling interviewer 'stupid' - video]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131577598.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Donald Trump abruptly ended a "Meet the Press" interview with Kristen Welker, accusing her and major news networks of being "crooked" and "stupid" after she pressed him for evidence of election fraud. Trump also defended his "anti-weaponisation fund" proposal, claiming political prosecutions have destroyed lives.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/thank-you-darling-trump-storms-out-of-nbc-interview-after-calling-interviewer-stupid-video/articleshow/131577598.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/thank-you-darling-trump-storms-out-of-nbc-interview-after-calling-interviewer-stupid-video/articleshow/131577598.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T09:47:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Priyanshi Rastogi</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131578180,imgsize-3937599.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[SpaceX IPO could turn a 27-year-old recovery boat engineer into a millionaire overnight: Meet the worker who invested 10% of every pay cheque]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131577520.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/spacex-ipo-could-turn-a-27-year-old-recovery-boat-engineer-into-a-millionaire-overnight-meet-the-worker-who-invested-10-of-every-pay-cheque/articleshow/131577520.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/spacex-ipo-could-turn-a-27-year-old-recovery-boat-engineer-into-a-millionaire-overnight-meet-the-worker-who-invested-10-of-every-pay-cheque/articleshow/131577520.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T09:07:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131577578,imgsize-606658.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Pilot, co-pilot killed as private aircraft crashes in Dominican Republic]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131576969.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/watch-pilot-co-pilot-killed-as-private-aircraft-crashes-in-dominican-republic/articleshow/131576969.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/watch-pilot-co-pilot-killed-as-private-aircraft-crashes-in-dominican-republic/articleshow/131576969.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T08:26:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131577058,imgsize-11304568.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Missiles rain across Israel's night sky as Iran launches fresh attacks after two months]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131576305.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran launched missiles at Israel, triggering air raid sirens and forcing millions to shelters. Israel claims to have intercepted the projectiles, but explosions were heard. Tehran warned of broader retaliation after an earlier Israeli strike. Meanwhile, former US President Trump urged restraint, reportedly persuading Prime Minister Netanyahu to hold off on immediate response.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/watch-missiles-rain-across-israels-night-sky-as-iran-launches-fresh-attacks-after-two-months/articleshow/131576305.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/watch-missiles-rain-across-israels-night-sky-as-iran-launches-fresh-attacks-after-two-months/articleshow/131576305.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T07:17:08+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131576321,imgsize-12634140.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Buildings turn to rubble after powerful 8.1 earthquake hits Philippines]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131576251.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A powerful 8.1-magnitude earthquake struck the Philippines, causing buildings to collapse and triggering tsunami warnings. High school and university structures were among those damaged, with viral videos showing crumbling buildings. Authorities issued tsunami warnings for the Philippines and neighboring Indonesia, with potential waves exceeding one meter.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/watch-buildings-turn-to-rubble-after-powerful-8-1-earthquake-hits-philippines/articleshow/131576251.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/watch-buildings-turn-to-rubble-after-powerful-8-1-earthquake-hits-philippines/articleshow/131576251.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T07:15:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Priyanshi Rastogi</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131576325,imgsize-3561481.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[FIFA World Cup 2026: Mass shooting near England's Kansas City base camp leaves 9 injured ahead of team arrival]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131575917.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A mass shooting in Kansas City left nine people injured just days before England's arrival for the 2026 FIFA World Cup, drawing renewed attention to tournament security preparations. Police stressed the incident was unrelated to the World Cup and occurred away from official venues. All victims are expected to survive as authorities continue investigating while teams prepare to arrive.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/fifa-world-cup/fifa-world-cup-2026-mass-shooting-near-englands-kansas-city-base-camp-leaves-9-injured-ahead-of-team-arrival/articleshow/131575917.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/fifa-world-cup/fifa-world-cup-2026-mass-shooting-near-englands-kansas-city-base-camp-leaves-9-injured-ahead-of-team-arrival/articleshow/131575917.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T05:44:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131576005,imgsize-1432025.cms"/></item></channel></rss>